		// Unicode Directional Formatting Characters
		// LRE	U+202A	LEFT-TO-RIGHT EMBEDDING
		// RLE	U+202B	RIGHT-TO-LEFT EMBEDDING
		// PDF	U+202C	POP DIRECTIONAL FORMATTING
